Proposal: The Lazarus State
Adoption index: 1
Authors: o

Amend rule 2485, "You can't take it with you", by changing its title to
"You Can't Take It With You", then by changing the paragraph beginning
"When a player is deregistered" to read, in full:

     When a player is deregistered, if eir Heir switch is not empty, e
     automatically pays all of eir Balance to the named player or
     organization. Otherwise, if eir Heir switch is empty, e may
     specify another player, an organization, or Agora and pay all of
     eir Balance to the specified player or organization. If the player
     does not do so within 3 days of deregistration and is not a player
     at that time, the Secretary CAN and SHALL cause that player to pay
     eir Balance to Agora, by announcement.
